This is a placeholder file. To create an actual Excel example, create a file with the following structure:

Column A: Empty
Column B: Location (required)
Column C: Branch Name (required)
Column D: Phone 1
Column E: Phone 2
Column F: Phone 3
Column G: Phone 4
Column H: IP Address

Example data:
| A | B        | C     | D           | E           | F | G | H             |
|---|----------|-------|-------------|-------------|---|---|---------------|
|   | القاهرة | فرع 1 | 01234567890 | 01123456789 |   |   | 192.168.1.1   |
|   | الجيزة  | فرع 2 | 01098765432 |             |   |   | 192.168.1.2   |
|   | الإسكندرية | فرع 3 | 01555555555 | 01266666666 | 01077777777 | | 192.168.1.3   |
